oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: The memorial to the Reverend Stephen Foreman, located in the Historic Brainerd Cemetery near Chattanooga, Tennessee.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The marker reads, "'He labored with the Cherokees and walked with God', The Reverend Stephen Foreman". He was born in 1807 in the Cherokee Nation and died in 1881.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Monuments & memorials; Cemeteries
